Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.88,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The great invasion of the State of Wei plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）魏(ぎ)の国への大攻略戦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:17.15,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Having been victorious in the first battle, the State of Qin Army was off to a great start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:16.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その初戦に勝利した秦国(しんこく)軍は\N順調な滑り出しとなった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:23.64,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But at this point, no one in the State of Qin had yet realized
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし このとき まだ\N秦国軍は 誰も気づいていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この遠征の先で 思いも寄らぬ\N大人物と対決することを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:29.39,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,that later on in this campaign they would confront an unimaginably grand figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.83,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,The people of Qin have invaded my kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（景湣王(けいびんおう)）\N秦の者どもが 我が国に侵攻し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:38.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虚中(きょちゅう) 虚西(きょさい)まで あっさりと陥落した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:39.22,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,and easily captured everything from central to West Xu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:46.87,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,But the reason I am not shaken whatsoever is because {\i1}you{\i0} are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:40.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が心胆が\N一切 震えることがないのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたがいるからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:50.99,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,Former member of the State of Zhao Three Great Devas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元趙国三大天(ちょうこく さんだいてん)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.52,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,Great General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗(れんぱ)大将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたが我が国に亡命してより３年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:57.23,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,It has been three years since you defected to my kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:01.46,Kingdom-Main,King,0,0,0,,There is nothing I have ever been more thankful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ほど\Nありがたく思ったことはないぞ
