Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N信(しん)の初陣となった蛇甘(だかん)平原の戦い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:14.29,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Several months before Xin's first campaign, the battle at Shegan Plain,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:20.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍 麃公(ひょうこう)と 魏国軍 呉慶(ごけい)が\N対決した あの戦いがあった年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:20.46,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,where the State of Qin Army led by Biao Gong fought the State of Wei Army led by Wu Qing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:26.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その数か月前にも 実は別の所で\N大きな戦が起こっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:26.39,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,there was actually another great battle happening elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:36.40,Kingdom-TL Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,( Flags - Zhao )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.45,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This battle went down in history
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「史記」にも\N記されている この戦いは―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:51.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,春秋時代においても\N極めて異質なものであった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.79,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,as a particularly odd battle, even for the Spring and Fall Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:57.09,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,That is because it was a clash between the State of Zhao Army and the State of Zhao Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:57.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 趙国軍 対 趙国軍の\N激突だったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（趙兵たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）ンンッ！\N（趙兵）ウワッ！
