Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:18.85,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Three Great Devas were the people celebrated as the three greatest generals of the State of Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）三大天とは\N趙国が誇る３人の大将軍である
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:24.16,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,They were heroes purported to be at the same level as the Six Great Generals of the State of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎(おうき)将軍ら秦国六大将軍と\N並び称される英雄で―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:29.83,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Their terrific fighting capability and military records roared throughout all of China.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:29.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのすさまじい武力と戦績により\N中国全土に名をとどろかせていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:35.84,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And one of those Three Great Devas was Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:35.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その三大天の１人こそが廉頗である
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.84,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Lian Po is coming! Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵）廉頗が来るぞ！ 止めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:46.33,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?! Our opponent is a general of our own state!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（歩兵Ａ）ど… どうなってんだ！\N相手は 同じ趙国軍なのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:51.79,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,And isn't Lian Po a hero of our state, Great General Lian Po?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（歩兵Ｂ）し… しかも 廉頗とは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が国の英雄\N廉頗大将軍ではないのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 どうして こんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.61,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Why the hell is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:02.01,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,General Lian Po isn't stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ａ）\N廉頗将軍 止まりません！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:05.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｂ）\Nくそ！ 楽乗(がくじょう)さま このままでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.12,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.68,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Lord Yue Chang, if this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）うろたえるな\N第４陣 左翼に差し込み 分断せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.74,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Do not panic.
