Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.65,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Fourth Formation, enter the left flank and split it apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.24,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.61,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,We have fought together for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）20年 共に戦ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:19.64,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,I have full knowledge of General Lian Po's fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗将軍の戦い方は\N全て 頭に入っている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:22.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｃ）\Nおお！ さすがは楽乗大将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I knew we could count on you, Great General Yue Chang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｂ）この戦 もらったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This war is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:29.35,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,General Lian Po, just what in the world are you thinking? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:29.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗将軍\N一体 何を考えておるのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.93,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The origin of this strange battle between comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）同士討ちという\Nこの異色の戦いの発端は―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この年\N趙国王に即位した悼襄王(とうじょうおう)にある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:39.04,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,is the man who was enthroned as King of Zhao this year, King Daoxiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:45.21,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,From when he was only the crowned prince, the ill-mannered King Daoxiang was frequently remonstrated by Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:45.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太子(たいし)のころより素行の悪い悼襄王は\Nしばしば 廉頗に いさめられていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:50.82,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This twisted king hated this from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆがんだ性格の王は\Nこれを心底 恨みに思っており―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国王に即位するや 遠征中の廉頗に\N大将軍剥奪を言い渡したのである
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.37,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,As soon as he took the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:57.13,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,he announced the revocation of Lian Po's title of general while Lian Po was out on campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:02.50,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Lian Po of course rejected this senseless dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:02.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理不尽な この更迭を\N廉頗は当然 拒否した
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:07.60,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Enraged by this, King Daoxiang raised an army of a remarkable 50,000 men,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:07.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これに激高した悼襄王は\Nなんと ５万の軍を起こし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.63,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and ordered Yue Chang to "defeat the traitor Lian Po".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:11.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“逆賊 廉頗を討て”と\N楽乗に命じたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:16.90,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Yue Chang was a member of the family called geniuses by the famed Zhuge Kongming,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽乗とは あの諸葛孔明(しょかつこうめい)をして\N天才と言わしめた楽毅(がくき)の一族である
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.64,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the Yueyi clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:23.94,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Yue Chang was Zhao's best general after Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:23.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽乗は\N廉頗に次ぐ趙国第２の将軍であり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その実力は ひそかに“廉頗を\Nしのぐのでは”とウワサされていた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:29.58,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was rumored that his ability secretly surpassed Lian Po's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:41.48,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,General Lian Po, I know how irrational it is, but this is the king's decree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:41.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）廉頗将軍 理不尽は\N承知ですが これは王の命です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:45.98,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Please General, allow me to take control of your soldiers and return to Handan for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:45.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか 将軍の兵を私に預け\N一度 邯鄲(かんたん)に お戻りください
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:46.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.63,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,General...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:52.40,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,If you do not comply, then I, Yue Chang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さもなくば この楽乗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:56.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力ずくで 将軍を\N邯鄲まで お連れせねばなりません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:56.18,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,must bring you to Handan by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:05:00.23,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Do you think you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:00.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぬに できるのか？ そんなことが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:04.73,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,I would not like to do it, but if I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりたくはありませんが\N必要とあらば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:10.99,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,We have a force of 50,000. General, you have 8,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）こちらは５万に対し\N将軍の兵は８千
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらに\Nあらがうすべは ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.74,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,There is no way for you to oppose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.24,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:21.21,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I will begin. Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:21.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしから仕掛けてやる　準備せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.33,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Wha?! General, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… 将軍 お待ちを！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.34,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Do you know what will happen to you if you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:28.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをしては\Nご自身が どうなるか…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:34.77,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,I cannot understand... Why he would do such a thing... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:34.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）理解に苦しむ\Nなぜ こんなバカなことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.47,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,Does he have some sort of plan...? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か思うところでもあったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.77,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,But it's too late now. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが もはや手遅れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:48.27,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,Now that we've crossed swords, I, Yue Chang, shall not hold back. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度 斬り結べば\Nこの楽乗 手加減は 一切せぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.46,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,The central unit led by General Lian Po has been destroyed! Destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ａ）廉頗将軍率いる\N中央部隊が崩壊！ 崩壊です！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（歓声）\N（部下Ｃ）か… 壊滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.83,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Th-The Lian Po unit was wiped out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗隊が！\N（部下Ｂ）よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.18,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:08.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｄ）\Nおお！ 廉頗将軍を討ち取ったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.56,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,We've defeated General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.76,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,The Yue Chang Army is the strongest in all of Zhao...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｂ）\Nこの楽乗軍こそ 趙国最強…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:29.27,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,So, how 'bout it, Yue Chang. Do ya give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうじゃ？ 楽乗　まいったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.41,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,I-I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まいりました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:38.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ！\Nそうじゃろう そうじゃろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.28,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Oh, ya do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎(りんこ)）はい 没収\N（楽乗軍将Ａ）クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.94,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Okay, confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗軍将Ｂ）れ… 廉頗将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.78,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことをして\N正気の沙汰ではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You must be out of your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You already cannot go back to the State of Zhao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗軍将Ｃ）\Nもはや 趙国には帰れませぬぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.42,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't plan on going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）おう 帰るつもりはない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗たち）ハッ…\N（廉頗）悼襄王… ありゃダメじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.00,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,King Daoxiang, that's really not gonna work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前の王も相当じゃったが\N今度は たまらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.45,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The last king wasn't great, but this one I really can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:06.06,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,There's nothing stupider than working under an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:05.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカの下で働くことほど\Nバカなことはないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ！\N（楽乗軍将Ｃ）廉頗将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.20,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,Is he intending to abandon his country? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）まさか 国を捨てる気で？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.33,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,I am disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）失望しましたぞ\N（廉頗）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.77,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Did it mean that little to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに軽いのですか？ これまで\N将軍の築き上げてきたものは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.95,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,All you've built up thus far as a general?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.94,Kingdom-Main,Yue,0,0,0,,Did you care that little of the State of Zhao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに軽かったのですか！\N趙国への思いは！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:36.47,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,My feelings towards war are much grander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:36.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）戦への思いのほうが\Nはるかに重い！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦で育まれ\N戦で全土に名をとどろかせ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:45.22,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I was raised on war, and made my name echo across the lands with war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:50.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強敵たちと出会い それらと\N全身全霊をささげて戦った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:50.70,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I met with great enemies and gave up all of my body and soul to fight with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が 廉頗の全てだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.29,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,War is what Lian Po is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.48,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:59.17,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,So why the hell was I stripped of my title of general?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:59.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを なにが大将剥奪か！\N（輪虎）うわぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神聖な戦場に 泥を\N投げ込むようなことを言いおって！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.49,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,How dare that idiot king sling mud onto the sacred battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:06.49,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And how dare those idiot retainers allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ王が！\Nそれを許す家臣もバカぞろいじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.24,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,That royal palace is nothing but an assembly hall of pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:10.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王宮は ブタの集会場か！\N（楽乗）ンンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽乗\N（楽乗）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.12,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Yue Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:16.36,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Your wars were pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぬの戦 なかなか良かったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このわしが\Nヒヤリとする場面が 何度かあった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:20.57,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,There were plenty of scenes that gave me chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ それでも しかし―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.60,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Well, even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.13,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,compared to those State of Qin guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国のあやつらに比べれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹八分目… いや\N腹六分目といったところだがのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:32.73,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You're just short of a full meal. A bit a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:38.63,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,These battlefields really are lonely without them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:38.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり ヤツらの消えた戦場は\N寂しいということか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:49.50,Kingdom-Thought,Yue,0,0,0,,It seems... that these men had different roles from the start. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:49.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楽乗）どうやら この方たちとは\N初めから 役者が違ったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:55.63,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And so, Lian Po took with him\N his long-time subordinate officers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）こうして 廉頗は―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生え抜きの将校たちを引き連れて\N魏の国に亡命した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.71,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and defected to the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:00.39,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Three years have passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:04.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから３年 廉頗は 一度も\N魏国軍を率いようとはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:04.78,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And Lian Po has never once tried to lead a State of Wei army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.31,Kingdom-TL Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,( Flag - Wei )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:08.95,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:08.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:15.04,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Great General has shown the intent to stand on the battlefield once again, hoisting the Wei flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:14.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏の旗を掲げて 再び\N大将軍は 戦場に立つ意思を示した
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.81,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,As a former member of the State of Zhao Three Great Devas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて 趙国三大天として―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎ら秦国六大将軍たちと\N互角に渡り合ってきた―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.82,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,he fought on par with Wang Qi and the other Six Great Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:25.85,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But now, what the monstrous general Lian Po has his eyes on is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,猛将 廉頗の目が\N今 捉えているのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:32.13,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,of course, the ones currently invading the State of Wei, the State of Qin Meng Ao Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:32.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 魏の国に侵攻中の\N秦国 蒙驁(もうごう)軍である
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.69,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊(かいしぼう)）\Nお待ちしておりました 殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.05,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You guys, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぬらか\Nさすがじゃ　もう嗅ぎつけたか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.76,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I should've known you'd catch wind of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:52.68,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,It was so mean of you not to tell us, the Four Heavenly Kings a thing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）ひどいな　四天王の僕らに\N相談ひとつないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:56.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヌハハハッ！\Nそのわりには 随分 うれしそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.27,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You seem quite happy nonetheless, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.02,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Indeed, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは そうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.70,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,When we thought of seeing your gallant figure in battle once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:04.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿の雄姿が 再び見られるとなると\N胸躍って 体が宙に浮きそうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.73,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,our hearts pounded and we felt like we'd fly right off the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.42,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Heavenly King Lun Hu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:10.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“廉頗四天王”\Nその響きも懐かしいわい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.69,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,that voice of yours really takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.29,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,It has been three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３年ぶりじゃが…
