Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎\N（輪虎）は～い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.30,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:28.19,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Your skills haven't rusted, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:28.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぬら 腕はサビておるまいな？\N（４人）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:28.80,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 輪虎\N（輪虎）はいは～い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.02,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.31,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.10,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The usual fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:39.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもどおりだ　先に出て 敵の\Nめぼしい将校の首を狩ってまいれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:39.29,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You go on ahead and hunt the heads of any outstanding enemy officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部下は 3,000ほどいればいいか？\N（輪虎）あ～ 大丈夫です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.13,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Would 3,000 subordinates be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:44.32,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Ah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:49.38,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,For such a mission, my 300-Man Unit would be plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その任なら\N僕の三百人隊くらいで十分です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.83,Kingdom - Episode Title,Xia,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\be1\fs80\an8\pos(311,7)}Lian Po
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:55.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）開戦より ひと月\N秦国軍の蒙驁本陣は―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.83,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,One month since the start of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:04.80,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The State of Qin Army's Meng Ao headquarters is approaching their third castle, the Jinli Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３つ目の城 近利関(きんりかん)に\Nさしかかっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.43,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）こ… こら 貴様ら！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.26,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Don't just climb our siege tower without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手に 井蘭車(せいらんしゃ)に上るな！\Nこれは わしらの物だろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:18.45,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,This is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:22.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）うるせえ！\Nこの井蘭者は みんなの物(もん)だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:22.65,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shaddup! This siege tower belongs to all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.90,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Like hell it—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽）ふざけ… アアッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.96,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,All right! We made it up the castle walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）しゃ！ 城壁に上ったぞ！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Go, Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け 飛信(ひしん)隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:35.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't let those Yufeng Unit idiots get all the credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊にばっか\N手柄を上げさせんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:41.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't let them win again! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁長）\Nそう何度もやらせるか　行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:56.10,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, the enemy's numbers are far higher than we anticipated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:56.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）信どの！\N敵の数が予想より はるかに多い！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Makes sense, this is the third time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:12:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）さすがに３度目だ\Nヤツらも準備してやがったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:01.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,They're getting better prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）\N我らと玉鳳隊でも これは厳しい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.19,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Even for both us and the Yufeng Unit, this is a hard fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.90,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, you bastards down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！ 下にいる てめえら！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:12.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit spacing out! Climb the siege tower on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボ～ッとしてねえで\N井蘭車で さっさと上ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:17.05,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There's a mountain of achievements up for grabs on these walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:17.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,城壁の上は 手柄の山だぞ！\N（どよめき）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.94,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,S-Stop! Don't climb that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,や… やめろ！ 上るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:32.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この井蘭車は\N人数制限があるんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:32.09,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,There's a limit to how many people can be on this siege tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.89,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Th-That many people is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんな大勢ではムリだ！\Nや… やめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.10,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.35,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,It'll collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壊れる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.19,Kingdom-Main,Meng,0,0,0,,Ah, this is pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）へ～え… これは楽ちん\N（番陽）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ 蒙恬 貴様まで！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.00,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Even you, you bastard, Meng Tian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）気をつけろ！ 来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Be careful! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.61,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,A heavy infantry unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁(おうほん)）重装歩兵隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.12,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Yufeng Unit! Get in rank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）玉鳳隊 隊列を組め
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃ！ 出番だぞ てめえら！\N（王賁）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's our turn, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（中鉄(ちゅうてつ)･田有(でんゆう)･竜川(りゅうせん)）ウオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.75,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The super-strong-three of the Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊 怪力三人衆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, head in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 中に入り込め！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原(すうげん)･去亥(きょがい)）よっしゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.01,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刺す音）\N（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刺す音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）へ～え…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.27,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect, because of all the experience they've gained {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:21.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに場数を踏んでるだけあって\Nそこらの歩兵隊より 格段に強い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.27,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,they're much stronger than those foot soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.73,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,And additionally... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,加えて そこに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤッ！\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.11,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,the captain and vice captain's extraordinary swordsmanship over there. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊長と副隊長のケタ外れの剣術\N飛信隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.50,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:46.97,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,They're a bit rough around the edges, but their destructive power is something to be reckoned with. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アラはあるが破壊力は相当なものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:52.01,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,It looks like General Wang Qi appointing them as a special unit wasn't just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王騎将軍から\N特殊部隊を任命されたのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伊達(だて)ではないってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.01,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,But even so... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,にしても…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）あの副長 ヤバすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.75,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,That vice captain is seriously dangerous. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.48,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）おら 行け行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ 何だ？ あやつら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.94,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,What are those guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:11.05,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,They're moving in the direction opposite the stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,階段と逆のほうへ進んでいくぞ\Nなっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.99,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Ah! Those guys, they have rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あやつら 縄を！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.45,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,C-Could it be they're intending to imitate our strategy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:17.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まさか\Nわしらの作戦をマネする気か！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:21.95,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Hey, you bastards! Do you have no pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！ 貴様ら そんなことまでして\N誇りはないのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:22.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:26.97,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Our pride is in not carrying any sorta cheap pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:26.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チンケな誇りなんざ\N持ち合わせてねえのが俺らの誇りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.65,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,You must be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！ そんな誇りがあるか\N（蒙恬）ハハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.50,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,What the hell sort of pride is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go, Long Chuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぞ 竜川！ しっかり持ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.76,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）あっ… ちょっと待て 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.26,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,They're already onto your plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その作戦は もうバレてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.27,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,They've got tons of enemy soldiers ready and waiting in front of the castle gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:42.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,城門前は\Nぎっしり 敵兵が待ち構えてるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや その前に そもそも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.77,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,No, even before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.99,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin! You're in the wrong place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの！ 場所がズレてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）そこは城門の上じゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.99,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,That's not above the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.38,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あちっ！\N（田有･中鉄）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ ウッ… ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:27.19,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どのーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.16,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣(きょうかい)）バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）あっ！ 動いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.37,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）\N生きてる！ 信どのは生きてるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.25,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.42,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ… まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.19,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:54.45,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,If he weren't such an idiot, he really could be a formidable rival for the Yufeng and Yuehua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:54.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでバカじゃなければ 本当に\N玉鳳 楽華(がくか)の強敵になるだろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:59.85,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is sorta the color of the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ でも―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが飛信隊の色といえば色か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… １人落ちてきたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,One person fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.89,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいてて…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）ぶっ殺せ！\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:12.98,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Oh, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い… いかん！\N信どのが袋のネズミに！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.82,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin is like a rat in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.33,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.11,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Er, go? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\Nえっ？ 行くって どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:23.91,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Please just run away for now, Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひ… ひとまず\N逃げてください 信どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.88,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,Ah, that's the State of Qin flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原）あっ！ あれは秦国の旗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They made it through the South castle wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）南の城壁を抜いたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,When did they...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの間に…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:47.33,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Against that showy siege tower, the enemy split up their soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:47.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,派手な井蘭車に対し\N敵は 兵を割いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:50.78,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,So it's natural they'd be short on hands. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかが手薄になっていたのは当然だ\Nしかも―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.89,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And what's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.03,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,That is Thousand-Man General Guo Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは郭備(かくび)千人将の部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:17:00.90,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Meaning someone of the core class of the Main Army has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:17:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 本軍主力級の実力者の\N登場というわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ…\Nボ～ッとしてる場合じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:09.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい てめえら さっさと下りてこい\Nまた手柄取られちまうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.88,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hurry the hell down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We're gonna get our achievements taken from us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）お… おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.91,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:15.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\Nその後 城内へ突入した飛信隊は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:19.42,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After that, the Feixin Unit coincidentally ran into an enemy's famed military commander and crushed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:18.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然 名のある武将と遭遇し\Nこれを撃破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:24.95,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,As a result, they rendered achievements greater than the Yufeng Unit or the Yuehua Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果的に 玉鳳隊 楽華隊よりも\N大きな武功を上げたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.77,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You bastards! We may not have gotten the general's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野郎ども！ 大将首は逃(のが)したが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:38.60,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,but let's set that aside for now and celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:39.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは ひとまず置いといて 祝杯だ\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.07,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was somewhat due to luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N運によるところもあったが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:46.55,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,but the Feixin Unit was honestly happy for their first military achievement in quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊は\Nこの久々の武功を素直に喜んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.99,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,But the way you fell was really something, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原）しかし\N隊長の落ちっぷりは見事だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,るせえ！ …つうか 竜川！\Nてめえ ちょっと来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.11,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.08,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And anyhow, Long Chuan, come here for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:18:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ！ あれで\Nケガしねえってのは さすが信だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.98,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Only you could end up unscathed after that, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:04.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田有）それより 井蘭車\N最後 車輪ぶっ壊れてたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.91,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But anyhow, that siege tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.09,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The wheels broke down in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.18,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It broke?! For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壊れた？ マジかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.60,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,Yeah. That old man from Yufeng was teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（松左(しょうさ)）ああ\N玉鳳のじいさん 涙目だったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\Nア～ハハッ！ ざまあみやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.00,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.92,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Oh, so they're the Feixin Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備）オッ… 彼らが飛信隊か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）うん？ 誰だ？ ありゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.91,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Lord Guo Bei, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下）\N郭備さま お急ぎを　軍議が…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:28.83,Kingdom-Main,Someone,0,0,0,,The war council!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有(りゅうゆう)）郭備？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:29.98,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Guo Bei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備）\Nすぐに行く　先に行っててくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.13,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.12,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:36.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永(でんえい)）郭備っていえば 今日\N大将首を挙げたっていう千人将じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:36.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Isn't Guo Bei the Thousand-Man General that took the enemy general's head today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.17,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,X-Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）し… 信\N（兵士）隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.13,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.33,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,So you're Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君が信か\Nフッ… 思ってたとおりの風貌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:50.14,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,You look just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.85,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,I've heard you used to be a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 下僕の出らしいな\N（信）ンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:58.73,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Ever since I heard that, I've had something I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備）それを耳にしてから\Nずっと伝えたいことがあった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンッ… んだよ？ 言ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.77,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What? Say it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ…\Nこの郭備も 下僕の出身だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.78,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,I, Guo Bei, was originally a servant as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.41,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Like you, I lost my parents to a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:11.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備）\N君と同じく 戦で親を亡くしてな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:15.64,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Since I was a small child, I worked as a servant for various different families,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:15.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幼少より\Nいろんな家の下僕を転々として―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:18.96,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,and was eventually taken in by my current family that originally didn't have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子供のいなかった今の家が\N養子にしてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.29,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Now I'm a comrade to those in the warrior class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 今は士族の仲間入りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:27.90,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,When I heard about your circumstances, it reminded me of my younger self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:27.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の境遇を聞き\N昔の自分を思い出してな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:31.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以来 ずっと君を応援していた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:31.30,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,I've been cheering you on ever since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:39.21,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,But to become a 300-Man General without any support, and so young, is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 何の後ろ盾もなく―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも その若さで\Nよく三百人将になったな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.91,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,You're really giving it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:43.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に頑張っている\N（信）えっ… いや 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:48.48,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,I was impressed by how you cut down that man Luan Tong at Guolong Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高狼(こうろう)城で\Nあの乱銅(らんどう)を斬ったことにも感心した
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.92,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Did you realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づいたか？\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:56.15,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, there weren't as many violations, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのおかげで\Nこの城では あんな蹂躙(じゅうりん)行為は―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:56.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほとんど なかったみたいだぞ\N（どよめき）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.70,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,All right, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったな 信！\N（信）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ah, h-hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）あっ… ちょ… ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:13.63,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,I took it upon myself to try to help you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭備）何か力になってやろうと\N勝手に思っていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ… 要らぬ世話だったようだ\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.20,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,but it seems I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:22.10,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,This unit is no fluke. Keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:21.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この隊は間違ってない\Nこのまま進め
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:27.11,Kingdom-Main,Guo,0,0,0,,Let's not lose to any nobles or warrior class families, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴士族なんかに負けるなよ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.67,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Meng Tian had mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）蒙恬が言ってたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:37.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知 武 勇\N全て そろった郭備千人将は―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:37.48,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Thousand-Man General Guo Bei is a popular general with intelligence, strength and bravery all in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人望も篤(あつ)く\N秦国軍の中でも極めて逸材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:41.82,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,An outstanding talent even among the State of Qin Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:46.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若い将校の中じゃ\N今いちばん将軍に近い武将だって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:46.71,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,And that among the young officers, he's the military commander closest to general right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:52.64,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Apparently he's already a close associate to Great General Meng Ao in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦いじゃ 既に 蒙驁大将軍の\N側近のひとりになってるらしいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:57.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He's a Thousand-Man General, but he's already an aide to a Great General...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:57.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有）千人将の身で\Nもう大将軍の側近って…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも まだ相当 若かったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:00.49,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,And he's still pretty young, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:03.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）\N下僕出身には 全然 見えなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.35,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,For someone that started as a servant, that's something I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.36,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,He's excelling past the warrior class people around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこらの貴族よりサマになってます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.86,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,But he still seemed like such a pleasant person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂(こう)）\Nだけど 全然 嫌みのない人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるんだな ああいう人も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.40,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,I guess there are guys like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.41,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Thousand-Man General Guo Bei... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,郭備千人将…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.53,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Thousand-Man General Guo Bei, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:28.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男性）郭備千人将 お待ちを\N（郭備）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:46.49,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Hm, who was next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）え～っと…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は誰だっけ？
